  "event_logo": "https://d8it4huxumps7.cloudfront.net/uploads/images/150x150/uploadedManual-698f3a78d0caf_esports_club.jpg",
  "description_html": "<p data-start=\"241\" data-end=\"258\">EVENT DESCRIPTION</p>\n<ul data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"650\">\n<li data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"331\">\n<p data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"331\">Teams will be divided into Groups based on number of registrations.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"332\" data-end=\"385\">\n<p data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"385\">Teams in each Group play the Group Stage matches.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"386\" data-end=\"489\">\n<p data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"489\">In Group Stage, each Team plays with every other Team in their respective group once (Round Robin).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"490\" data-end=\"590\">\n<p data-start=\"492\" data-end=\"590\">2 teams from each group will advance to Play-offs (may change with respect to number of groups).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"591\" data-end=\"650\">\n<p data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"650\">Play-offs will be conducted in Double-Elimination format.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"655\" />\n<p data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"665\">RULEBOOK</p>\n<p data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"685\">POINTS CALCULATION</p>\n<ul data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"821\">\n<li data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"739\">\n<p data-start=\"689\" data-end=\"739\">Teams will be ranked in their respective groups.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"821\">\n<p data-start=\"742\" data-end=\"821\">Teams will be allocated points based on points earned at the end of each match.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"826\" />\n<p data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"843\">CS MATCH POINTS</p>\n<ul data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"1005\">\n<li data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"873\">\n<p data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"873\">Victory Round: +2 points</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"901\">\n<p data-start=\"876\" data-end=\"901\">Match Booyah: +2 points</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"946\">\n<p data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"946\">WIN: (7 multiplied by 2) + 2 = 16 points</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"1005\">\n<p data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"1005\">LOSS (with x rounds victory): (x multiplied by 2) points</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1010\" />\n<p data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1025\">GAME SETTINGS</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1271\">\n<li data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1048\">\n<p data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1048\">Mode: Clash Squad</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1071\">\n<p data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1071\">Store: Random Buff</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1086\">\n<p data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1086\">Rounds: 13</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1112\">\n<p data-start=\"1089\" data-end=\"1112\">Character Skills: OFF</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1113\" data-end=\"1136\">\n<p data-start=\"1115\" data-end=\"1136\">Gun Attributes: OFF</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1161\">\n<p data-start=\"1139\" data-end=\"1161\">Ammo: Unlimited Ammo</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1162\" data-end=\"1180\">\n<p data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1180\">Air Drops: OFF</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1198\">\n<p data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1198\">Loadouts: OFF</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1218\">\n<p data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1218\">Others: Default</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1219\" data-end=\"1271\">\n<p data-start=\"1221\" data-end=\"1226\">Maps:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1271\">\n<li data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1240\">\n<p data-start=\"1231\" data-end=\"1240\">Bermuda</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1243\" data-end=\"1256\">\n<p data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1256\">Purgatory</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1259\" data-end=\"1271\">\n<p data-start=\"1261\" data-end=\"1271\">Kalahari</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1273\" data-end=\"1276\" />\n<p data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1305\">RESTRICTIONS AND VIOLATIONS</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1660\">\n<li data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1423\">\n<p data-start=\"1309\" data-end=\"1423\">Gloo Wall Breaking is NOT Allowed, but Wall Climbing is allowed<br data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1375\" />(Negative round result in case of violation)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1424\" data-end=\"1472\">\n<p data-start=\"1426\" data-end=\"1472\">NO Zone Packing and Blocking with Gloo Walls</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1526\">\n<p data-start=\"1475\" data-end=\"1526\">House or Rooftop Climbing is strictly NOT Allowed</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1660\">\n<p data-start=\"1529\" data-end=\"1573\">Use of the following is strictly prohibited:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1660\">\n<li data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1588\">\n<p data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1588\">Grenades</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1591\" data-end=\"1606\">\n<p data-start=\"1593\" data-end=\"1606\">Flash Bangs</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1625\">\n<p data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1625\">Freeze Bombs</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1628\" data-end=\"1646\">\n<p data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1646\">Smoke Grenades</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1649\" data-end=\"1660\">\n<p data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1660\">Turrets</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1665\" />\n<p data-start=\"1667\" data-end=\"1678\">MATCH RULES</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1680\" data-end=\"2285\">\n<li data-start=\"1680\" data-end=\"1750\">\n<p data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1750\">Gun properties will be disabled throughout Group and Final stages.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1751\" data-end=\"1825\">\n<p data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1825\">Use of emulators (Bluestacks, Nox, Memu, etc.) and iPad is prohibited.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1868\">\n<p data-start=\"1828\" data-end=\"1868\">Use of illegal programs is prohibited.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"2002\">\n<p data-start=\"1871\" data-end=\"1919\">Use of additional or supporting devices such as:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"2002\">\n<li data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"1934\">\n<p data-start=\"1924\" data-end=\"1934\">Gamepads</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2002\">\n<p data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"2002\">Controllers (R1, L1 buttons, etc.)<br data-start=\"1973\" data-end=\"1976\" />is strictly forbidden.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2003\" data-end=\"2141\">\n<p data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2062\">Flaming, cheating, or toxic behaviour is not tolerated.</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2065\" data-end=\"2141\">\n<li data-start=\"2065\" data-end=\"2092\">\n<p data-start=\"2067\" data-end=\"2092\">Warnings will be issued</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2095\" data-end=\"2141\">\n<p data-start=\"2097\" data-end=\"2141\">Repeated offenses will result in penalties</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2205\">\n<p data-start=\"2144\" data-end=\"2205\">Teaming is prohibited. Any team involved will be penalized.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2285\">\n<p data-start=\"2208\" data-end=\"2285\">The match will continue even if a player disconnects or faces in-game errors.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2287\" data-end=\"2290\" />\n<p data-start=\"2292\" data-end=\"2302\">DISCLAIMER</p>\n<p data-start=\"2304\" data-end=\"2324\">FINALITY OF DECISION</p>\n<p data-start=\"2326\" data-end=\"2350\">All decisions regarding:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2456\">\n<li data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2378\">\n<p data-start=\"2353\" data-end=\"2378\">Interpretation of rules</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2379\" data-end=\"2401\">\n<p data-start=\"2381\" data-end=\"2401\">Player eligibility</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2402\" data-end=\"2427\">\n<p data-start=\"2404\" data-end=\"2427\">Tournament scheduling</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2456\">\n<p data-start=\"2430\" data-end=\"2456\">Penalties for misconduct</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"2458\" data-end=\"2535\">lie solely with the Tournament Admin (Esports Team). All decisions are final.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2540\" />\n<p data-start=\"2542\" data-end=\"2554\">RULE CHANGES</p>\n<p data-start=\"2556\" data-end=\"2712\">These rules may be amended, modified, or supplemented by the Tournament Admin (Esports Team) from time to time to ensure fair play and tournament integrity.</p>",
